snippet.title: Strike Force Heroes - Fan Art Collab
snippet.description:
Thanks to the amazing community that created all this fan art before the game was even released!

Everyone has been such a huge inspiration to make the game what it is today, and we're super grateful for all the love!

If you're new, join the community here:
http://www.tinyurl.com/SFHdiscord

Song: Chris Barker Guitarist
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UptGXpeO_ZQ
